video.title: Black Money Love
video.synopsis: After a cop's fiancée and a jewelry designer's father are found dead together, the two bereaved ones face a perilous aftermath of a theft gone wrong.

episodes.synopsis: As he recovers from the shock of his loss, Ömer looks for clues behind an accident connected to Sibel's family.
